    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Not sure if this is the cause of the problem, but I got this issue only after installing <strong>JVM Monitor</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>Uninstalling JVM Monitor solved the issue for me.</p>\n"
