    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Copy Pasting @Lichtamberg's comments to gotoalberto's answer</p>\n\n<p><strong>Works also for Java 1.8:</strong> </p>\n\n<pre><code># in ~/.zshrc and ~/.bashrc\n\nexport JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_92.jdk/Contents/Home \nexport PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This fixed my issue on java 8.</p>\n"
