    "body" : "<p>⚠️ <strong>For JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA</strong>: Go to  <code>Help -&gt; Edit Custom Properties...</code>. Create the file if it asks you to create it. To disable the error message paste the following to the file you created:</p>\n<pre><code>idea_rt\nidea.no.launcher=true\n</code></pre>\n<p>This will take effect on the restart of the IntelliJ.</p>\n"
